videos.description: Tony Kornheiser and Michael Wilbon debate whether Duke coach Mike Krzyzewski's decision to temporarily ban his players from the locker room and forbid them from wearing team apparel is an effective measure.
videos.headline: Is Coach K's discipline something or nothing?
